Reasoning: 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is the most likely category as the paper is about Simgrid, a toolkit for simulating large scale distributed systems. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also likely as Simgrid can be used to simulate networked systems. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as Simgrid can be used to simulate control systems. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper discusses improving the quality of the software. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as Simgrid is a software toolkit.
